name: Agent Run Feedback
query:
SELECT
    f.`agent` AS "Agent:Link/Agent:200",
    MAX(f.`provider`) AS "Provider:Link/AI Provider:150",
    MAX(f.`model`) AS "Model:Link/AI Model:150",
    SUM(CASE WHEN f.`feedback` = 'Thumbs Up' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "Thumbs Up:Int:120",
    SUM(CASE WHEN f.`feedback` = 'Thumbs Down' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "Thumbs Down:Int:120",
    COUNT(f.`name`) AS "Total Feedback:Int:120",
    CONCAT(
        ROUND(
            (SUM(CASE WHEN f.`feedback` = 'Thumbs Up' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(f.`name`)) * 100, 
        1), 
        '%%'
    ) AS "Satisfaction Rate:Data:120"
FROM
    `tabAgent Run Feedback` f
WHERE
    DATE(f.`creation`) BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)s
    AND (%(agent)s IS NULL OR %(agent)s = '' OR f.`agent` = %(agent)s)
GROUP BY
    f.`agent`
ORDER BY
    f.`agent` ASC
